{"text_id":234546,"tokens":["When"," making"," important"," decisions",","," many"," people"," think"," that"," relying"," solely"," on"," their"," own"," intuition"," and"," knowledge"," is"," the"," best"," approach","."," However",","," extensive"," research"," has"," shown"," that"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," can"," be"," the"," most"," effective"," path"," to"," making"," a"," well","-","informed"," decision","."," Having"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," opinions"," and"," perspectives"," can"," help"," provide"," insight"," and"," clarity"," into"," a"," situation"," that"," would"," otherwise"," be"," missed","."," I"," have"," personally"," experienced"," this"," situation"," many"," times"," and"," know"," firsthand"," the"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," when"," making"," important"," decisions",".","\n","One"," of"," the"," major"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," is"," the"," ability"," to"," consider"," multiple"," perspectives","."," Recently",","," I"," was"," faced"," with"," a"," difficult"," decision"," about"," a"," job"," offer","."," The"," offer"," was"," very"," attractive"," in"," terms"," of"," salary"," and"," perks"," but"," the"," proposed"," location"," was"," a"," downside","."," To"," decide"," whether"," I"," should"," accept"," the"," job",","," I"," sought"," advice"," from"," numerous"," sources"," \u2013"," my"," parents",","," friends",","," and"," colleagues","."," Each"," provided"," a"," different"," perspective"," and"," they"," all"," helped"," me"," powerfully"," form"," an"," opinion","."," My"," parents"," focused"," on"," the"," stability"," and"," superiority"," of"," the"," job",","," my"," friends"," focused"," on"," the"," lifestyle"," aspects",","," and"," my"," colleagues"," focused"," on"," the"," career"," growth"," opportunities","."," Through"," considering"," these"," perspectives",","," I"," was"," able"," to"," make"," an"," informed"," decision"," that"," I"," was"," happy"," with",".","\n","In"," addition"," to"," considering"," multiple"," perspectives",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," can"," also"," help"," to"," build"," self","-","awareness","."," We"," often"," view"," ourselves"," and"," our"," situations"," through"," rose","-","colored"," glasses"," and"," make"," decisions"," without"," fully"," compre","hending"," our"," own"," motivations","."," By"," observing"," other"," people"," outside"," of"," our"," situation",","," we"," can"," better"," understand"," how"," our"," decisions"," will"," effect"," our"," livelihoods","."," This"," includes"," understanding"," how"," a"," new"," job"," aligns"," with"," our"," career"," ambitions",","," the"," pros"," and"," cons"," of"," relocating"," to"," a"," different"," geographic"," area",","," and"," even"," the"," impact"," that"," a"," difficult"," decision"," will"," have"," on"," our"," mental"," health","."," ","\n","Overall",","," I"," strongly"," believe"," that"," the"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," when"," making"," important"," decisions"," are"," invaluable","."," It"," allows"," us"," to"," evenly"," consider"," multiple"," perspectives",","," build"," self","-","awareness",","," and"," make"," an"," informed"," decision"," which"," aligns"," with"," our"," individual"," goals"," and"," interests","."," Through"," my"," own"," experiences",","," I"," have"," come"," to"," understand"," the"," importance"," of"," gathering"," advice"," from"," my"," key"," supporters"," \u2013"," both"," near"," and"," far"," \u2013"," before"," I"," make"," any"," important"," decisions","."," This"," has"," helped"," guide"," me"," to"," make"," decisions"," I"," am"," happy"," with"," and"," set"," me"," on"," the"," path"," for"," a"," successful"," and"," fulfilling"," future","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"text-davinci-003","label":1}